description: Demolition of 6-44 Station Road and all but the facade of 6-12 Station Road; erection of two buildings comprising 25 storeys (plus partial basement and mezzanine) and 21 storeys (plus mezzanine) to provide 232 residential units and 947 M2 of commercial floorspace (for use within Class A1,A2,A3,A4 or A5) ; new public square including area for retail use, works to church car park , cycle parking, disabled parking and sustainable energy measures.
